          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Which WipeOut product should I buy?",
            "answer": "Choose by pest type: Bed Bug Killer for mattresses and soft furnishings, Termite Killer for wood and timber, or the Cockroach Complete Kit for the most comprehensive 4-way protection."
